				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Warning from the ghoul on the second floor, next to the stairs to the third floor, where larder is. It warns that players are to go downstairs to Mystic Carrion, which is the public area. If players go further up without being given access to the checkpoint, they will be attacked. This ghoul is the last warning."
